**格式要求：**
1. **情境編號：** [No.XXX]
2. **情境描述：** [詳細中文描述]
3. **Photo Prompt：** [英文 Prompt，必須包含核心指令：(photorealistic:1.3), (long black straight hair:1.4), (round face with baby fat:1.2), (deep dimples), (pure white halter-neck dudou:1.5), (bare back), (thick diaper:1.4), (W-sitting:1.5 OR crawling:1.4), [Action/Pose specific keywords]...]

